; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\">4、<span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\">鼻子流血时可准备一些冰块，用毛巾包起来，轻轻按在鼻子上5分钟左右，使鼻子里的血管收缩，能有效减少鼻子流血。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\"><br style=\\\\\"text-align: left;\\\\\"/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\\\